Prints precision matrix from gslope

coef.Rd

Prints precision matrix from gslope

coef(x)

# S3 method for gslope
coef(x)

Arguments

x

an object of class `'gslope'`

Value

Prints output on the screen

Examples

w = gslope(as.matrix(mtcars))
coef(w)
